My 62 Crew Cab (Dec '61 built) has flashers, and it appears to be stock,
as far as the switch, relay, and wiring...fwiw...

>  I believe emergency flashers started for the 63 model year.  They were
> optional in Euro spec buses, standard on US spec ones.  the wiring
> diagram for them is the the 63-67 Bentley, but look in the accessories
> section of the electrical chapter for the 63-65 e-flasher wiring, it is
> not in the regular wiring diagram.


